To run the MVC and see it working

Step 1: Pull down the coolshopMVC and make it available in your local machine

Step 2: Run the SQL 

Step 3: Go to http://localhost/coolshopMVC/Admin/customer.php

Step 4: Now you can see the customer being Display

Notes:

How the customer was integrated into the framework;

a. customerController.php
b. personController.php (for individual customer)
c. Own HTML Master page
d. Added an image

Model
a. customers.php
b. person.php (individual customer)

View
customers.php

Admin
a. new DB object and instantiation of the new Customer Object from customer controller

 
 What still needs to be done;
 
 1. Login and Logout to Admin section.
 2. Add new customer and edit.
